<div class="thumbnail-container" style="padding-bottom: 50%;">
<h1 class="jeg_post_title"><a href="https://www.avrupahaber10.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/4515830453734031293.jpeg"><img alt="" class="attachment-jnews-750x375 size-jnews-750x375 wp-post-image" height="261" src="https://www.avrupahaber10.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/4515830453734031293.jpeg" title="Türkiye, T. Kürdistanı ve Suriye - Rojava&#8217;da depremin dördüncü gününde hayatını kaybedenlerin sayısı her an artıyor 1" width="500" /></a>&nbsp;</h1><h1 class="jeg_post_title">AGEB: Renforçons la solidarité avec notre peuple qui a souffert du tremblement de terre!</h1>
<div class="jeg_meta_container"><div class="jeg_post_meta jeg_post_meta_1">
<div class="meta_left">
<div class="jeg_meta_date">
