</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt;"><span lang="en-GB">great.</span></span></span></p>
<p class="western" lang="de-DE" style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-top: 0.21cm; text-indent: 0cm;">
<span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">Our people
living in Kurdistan, which the Turkish fascism only thinks of during
election periods, have been ignored</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 2.0pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">for
years with policies of annihilation and denial, and their vital
resources have been deliberately destroyed by war policies. Although</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.8pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">Turkey</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.8pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">is</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.8pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">an</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.8pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">earthquake</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.8pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
