</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">of</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.8pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">building</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.8pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">earthquake-resistant
buildings,</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 4.0pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">those</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 4.0pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
