</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">the</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.6pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">fact</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">that</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">the</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">magnitude</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.6pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">of</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.6pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
</span></span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span lang="en-GB">the</span></span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5pt;"><span lang="en-GB">
